            <lg xml:id="TK140">
<l>ulakattō ṭoṭṭa voḻukal palakaṟṟuṅ</l>
<l>kallā raṟivilā tār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have not studied conduct as connected with the world,</l>
<l>though they've studied much, are ignorant.</l>
